<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>الْحِكَايَةُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٧٥٠. احْكِ بِـ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«أَيٍّ»</span> مَا لِمَنْكُورٍ سُئِلْ … عَنْهُ بِهَا فِي الْوَقْفِ، أَوْ حِينَ تَصِلْ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٧٥١. وَوَقْفاً احْكِ مَا لِمَنْكُورٍ بِـ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«مَنْ»</span> … وَالنُّونَ حَرِّكْ مُطْلَقاً وَأَشْبِعَنّْ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٧٥٢.<span style="color:#006d98"> وَقُلْ:</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«مَنَانِ؟ وَمَنَيْنِ؟»</span> بَعَدَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«لِي … إِلْفَانِ بِابْنَيْنِ»</span>، وَسَكِّنْ تَعْدِلِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٧٥٣. وَقُلْ لِمَنْ قَالَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«أَتَتْ بِنْتٌ»</span>: <span style="color:#6c6c00">«مَنَهْ؟»</span> … وَالنُّونُ قَبْلَ تَا الْمُثَنَّى مُسْكَنَهْ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٧٥٤. وَالْفَتْحُ نَزْرٌ، وَصِلِ التَّا وَالْأَلِفْ … بِـ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«مَنْ»</span> بِإِثْرِ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«ذَا بِنِسْوَةٍ كَلِفْ»</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٧٥٥.<span style="color:#006d98"> وَقُلْ:</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«مَنُونَ؟ وَمَنِينَ؟»</span> مُسْكِنَا … إِنْ قِيلَ: <span style="color:#6c6c00">«جَا قَوْمٌ لِقَوْمٍ فُطَنَا»</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٧٥٦. وَإِنْ تَصِلْ فَلَفْظُ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«مَنْ»</span> لَا يَخْتَلِفْ … وَنَادِرٌ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«مَنُونَ»</span> فِي نَظْمٍ عُرِفْ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٧٥٧. وَالْعَلَمَ احْكِيَنَّهُ مِنْ بَعْدِ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«مَنْ»</span> … إِنْ عَرِيَتْ مِنْ عَاطِفٍ بِهَا اقْتَرَنْ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>* * *<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>